制度、设立派出看护妇会协助防疫的历程。                                                                      　　明治18年，日本首个护士培训学校成立。坎坷命运下早成单亲母亲的一之濑凛（见上爱 饰），与自幼被遗弃、在教会庇护下长大的大家直美（上坂树里 饰），在这里命运般相遇。她们与同学们一同接受尚在摸索中的护理教育，思索“护理是什么”“面对病人意味着什么”。毕业后，凛和直美各自经历被逐出岗位、卷入事件等波折，却在霍乱与痢疾肆虐之时再次携手，直面瘟疫。<\/p>","vod_play_from":"lzm3u8","vod_play_server":"no","vod_play_note":"","vod_play_url":"第01集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260330\/7812_d67f5e23\/index.m3u8#第02集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260331\/7856_28ce6a68\/index.m3u8#第03集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260401\/7923_6e86d722\/index.m3u8#第04集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260402\/8019_241e8ac1\/index.m3u8#第05集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260403\/8107_f6d8d271\/index.m3u8#第06集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260406\/8277_7fbfcbe3\/index.m3u8#第07集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260407\/8313_54eb499e\/index.m3u8#第08集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260408\/8366_b7eca268\/index.m3u8#第09集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260409\/8412_be68af71\/index.m3u8#第10集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260410\/8493_4c571c43\/index.m3u8#第11集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260413\/8627_b7e98811\/index.m3u8#第12集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn31.com\/20260414\/5042_6264ad81\/index.m3u8#第13集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260415\/8749_767ca856\/index.m3u8#第14集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260416\/8789_fd01302a\/index.m3u8#第15集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn31.com\/20260417\/5282_8bc8aef3\/index.m3u8#第16集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn31.com\/20260420\/5491_3856bdba\/index.m3u8#第17集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260421\/9082_940a05b1\/index.m3u8#第18集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260422\/9129_e660d6e0\/index.m3u8#第19集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260423\/9169_345481ab\/index.m3u8#第20集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260424\/9232_b5ea936a\/index.m3u8#第21集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260427\/9400_ad673647\/index.m3u8#第22集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn31.com\/20260428\/6011_0c634137\/index.m3u8#第23集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260429\/9517_9dd5082c\/index.m3u8#第24集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn27.com\/20260430\/9559_ac00498a\/index.m3u8#第25集$https:\/\/v.lzcdn31.com\/20260501\/6081_acdd7e5c\/index.m3u8